Dialogue: 10,0:00:03.47,0:00:04.53,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Was it all a lie?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:05.40,0:00:06.97,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:06.97,0:00:07.93,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:07.93,0:00:10.20,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Did you have a bad dream ag—
Dialogue: 10,0:00:10.20,0:00:11.07,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:16.41,0:00:18.75,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Were you just pretending to have a heart?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:19.40,0:00:20.45,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Pretending?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:21.00,0:00:22.21,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,What do you mean by preten—
Dialogue: 10,0:00:22.21,0:00:23.63,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,It means lying!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:23.63,0:00:25.96,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,It means saying things you don't mean!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:29.34,0:00:30.91,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:31.39,0:00:35.72,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,My job is to be useful to you and make you happy.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:36.03,0:00:38.74,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,That's the motivation behind all my actions.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:41.03,0:00:44.66,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,When you said you had a heart, did you mean it? {? the かも}
Dialogue: 10,0:00:45.69,0:00:50.78,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Did you say that only because you\ngenuinely believe you have one?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:55.28,0:00:55.79,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:56.09,0:00:57.70,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Then here's an order for you!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:57.70,0:00:59.39,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Stop pretending you have a heart!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:59.39,0:01:01.29,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Stop trying to make me happy!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:06.35,0:01:06.84,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:11.01,0:01:12.47,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Why did you lie to me?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:12.47,0:01:15.23,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,I have already answered that inquiry.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:15.83,0:01:17.35,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Do you love me?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:18.90,0:01:20.85,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,As you are now,
Dialogue: 10,0:01:23.99,0:01:25.36,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,I hate you.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:37.87,0:01:38.95,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Don't follow me!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:28.65,0:03:30.44,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,I'm a super high-spec model!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:32.22,0:03:33.81,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Was it all a lie?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:34.40,0:03:36.45,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Her smiles... Her laughter...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:37.11,0:03:40.41,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Everything we went through...\nEverything she showed me...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:40.78,0:03:42.03,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Was it all a lie?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:16.52,0:04:18.48,Default,Ryuuji,0,0,0,,You sure he's okay?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:18.48,0:04:20.33,Default,Ryuuji,0,0,0,,Whatever happened, it was serious.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:20.33,0:04:21.15,Default,Ririka,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:21.15,0:04:23.67,Default,Ririka,0,0,0,,When we found him sprawled out on the road,
Dialogue: 10,0:04:23.67,0:04:25.83,Default,Ririka,0,0,0,,I thought I was gonna have a heart attack.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:29.65,0:04:31.45,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,Thanks, you two.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:31.45,0:04:34.30,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,I'll handle things from here.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:34.30,0:04:35.21,Default,Ryuuji,0,0,0,,You sure?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:35.21,0:04:36.17,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:36.17,0:04:38.87,Default,Ririka,0,0,0,,Okay, we'll give you two some space.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:55.54,0:04:57.17,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,Did you two have a fight?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:00.74,0:05:01.81,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Minamo...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:02.85,0:05:04.56,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Did you know all along?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:07.35,0:05:08.32,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,Know what?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:09.16,0:05:11.98,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,No, {\i1}I{\i0} should've known all along.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:11.98,0:05:13.83,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,She's nothing but a Humanoid.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:15.29,0:05:18.58,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,There's no way {\i1}a thing like that{\i0}\ncould possibly have a heart.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:20.21,0:05:22.93,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,All she was ever doing was\nanalyzing vast amounts of data;
Dialogue: 10,0:05:22.93,0:05:26.47,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,processing contextual information,\nresponding to external stimuli,
Dialogue: 10,0:05:27.24,0:05:29.73,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,all to output the most optimal solution.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:30.26,0:05:33.77,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,She laughed when she was supposed to,\ngot angry when she was supposed to,
Dialogue: 10,0:05:34.52,0:05:36.92,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,faithfully executing her programming
Dialogue: 10,0:05:36.92,0:05:40.06,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,to perfectly tailor her words\nand manufacture her expressions.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:42.33,0:05:45.61,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,That's all Humanoids are.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:56.17,0:05:57.47,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,You know what I think?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:58.03,0:06:02.63,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,I think that's no different\nfrom what we humans do.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:03.03,0:06:04.62,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,I know I'm like that, at least.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:05.13,0:06:10.39,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,I watch other people's expressions,\nthink carefully about what I should say,
Dialogue: 10,0:06:10.39,0:06:13.94,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,and choose my words and actions\nbased on how they look and act.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:15.50,0:06:17.94,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,Who can really say what it means to have a heart?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:19.74,0:06:22.85,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,But I think all of us sometimes\ndo unexplainable things,
Dialogue: 10,0:06:22.85,0:06:25.51,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,things we don't even understand ourselves,
Dialogue: 10,0:06:25.51,0:06:28.95,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,just because it's what our heart tells us is right.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:30.92,0:06:34.08,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,So if you ask me, I think you were right all along,
Dialogue: 10,0:06:34.69,0:06:38.09,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,and that Atri{**-chan} really does have a heart.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:38.81,0:06:43.09,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,But I think she's doubting herself.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:44.08,0:06:47.82,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,It must be something really scary for her,\nrealizing she has a heart.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:52.74,0:06:53.55,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Ow...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:53.55,0:06:56.29,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,Sorry! I figured you'd want something warm.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:56.29,0:06:58.56,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,Should I have let it cool a bit more?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:58.98,0:07:00.52,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:02.33,0:07:04.65,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,This is just right.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:12.02,0:07:12.91,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,Morning!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:13.53,0:07:17.42,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,I just went to go check on Atri{**-chan},\nand she was doing fine.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:18.01,0:07:19.50,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,She said she'd be at school.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:20.45,0:07:21.63,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:22.26,0:07:27.06,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,I'll tell everyone you're out with a cold, okay?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:27.06,0:07:29.36,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,No, I'll go too.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:29.36,0:07:30.14,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:30.14,0:07:34.26,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,It'd be unfair to everyone who showed up\nif their teacher called in sick.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:34.26,0:07:35.32,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:35.32,0:07:36.44,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Besides,
Dialogue: 10,0:07:37.31,0:07:40.90,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,I can't exactly get away with avoiding Atri forever.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:42.31,0:07:44.32,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,I was hoping you'd say that.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:44.68,0:07:46.79,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,And so I brought your uniform!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:50.51,0:07:51.81,Default,Miyo,0,0,0,,Sure is coming down hard, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:51.81,0:07:52.82,Default,Ririka,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:53.34,0:07:53.95,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:54.41,0:07:56.16,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,{*}Mr. Natsuki{*Natsuki-sensei}!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:58.06,0:07:58.96,Default,Ririka,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:58.96,0:08:00.87,Default,Ririka,0,0,0,,Where's Atrin?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:01.73,0:08:02.95,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Is she not here?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:02.95,0:08:05.24,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,She said she'd come though...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:11.13,0:08:12.33,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:12.33,0:08:14.47,Default,Catherine,0,0,0,,No return address.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:14.47,0:08:19.31,Default,Catherine,0,0,0,,It's a report on the recall of\nYamasaki Factory's fourth-generation models.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:19.77,0:08:21.64,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Yamasaki Factory...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:22.73,0:08:23.98,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,So it's about Atri!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:23.98,0:08:25.27,Default,Catherine,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:25.27,0:08:29.78,Default,Catherine,0,0,0,,This probably came from\nsomeone who knows she's here.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:31.71,0:08:32.75,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Aggravated battery?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:33.29,0:08:37.45,Default,Catherine,0,0,0,,"In defiance of its user's orders,\nthe unit in question trespassed into a school
Dialogue: 10,0:08:37.45,0:08:39.68,Default,Catherine,0,0,0,,and severely injured one of its students." {almost certain in the game it was only one student, but perhaps this is safer in case the anime shows something different}
Dialogue: 10,0:08:39.68,0:08:40.79,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Atri did that?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:40.79,0:08:44.42,Default,Catherine,0,0,0,,Who knows if she really was "the unit in question."
Dialogue: 10,0:08:44.86,0:08:49.68,Default,Catherine,0,0,0,,But her model only ever sold\na grand total of 58 units.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:49.68,0:08:52.13,Default,Catherine,0,0,0,,They were all immediately recalled,
Dialogue: 10,0:08:52.13,0:08:57.18,Default,Catherine,0,0,0,,but a single unit, the one responsible\nfor the incident, broke out and went missing.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:57.84,0:09:01.48,Default,Catherine,0,0,0,,Naturally, Yamasaki Factory covered that up,
Dialogue: 10,0:09:01.48,0:09:06.88,Default,Catherine,0,0,0,,but all the bad press still tanked the demand\nfor Humanoids, and the company went under.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:06.88,0:09:09.34,Default,Catherine,0,0,0,,The missing unit never did get recovered either.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:09.92,0:09:12.24,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,And you're saying that unit was Atri?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:12.24,0:09:13.91,Default,Catherine,0,0,0,,There's no proof.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:14.39,0:09:17.73,Default,Catherine,0,0,0,,This report could just be a big crock of bull.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:17.73,0:09:21.92,Default,Catherine,0,0,0,,But I'm responsible for these kiddos' safety,\nso I can't just pretend I never saw it.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:22.94,0:09:25.37,Default,Catherine,0,0,0,,When she came by earlier,
Dialogue: 10,0:09:25.37,0:09:29.28,Default,Catherine,0,0,0,,I told her I couldn't risk letting her\ninto the school and turned her away.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:32.28,0:09:35.75,Default,Catherine,0,0,0,,You should get going too.\nI can handle things here on my own.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:35.75,0:09:38.34,Default,Catherine,0,0,0,,I still owe you one, after all.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:40.06,0:09:41.14,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:50.84,0:09:53.64,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,{\i1}Atri turned violent?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:54.77,0:09:57.10,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is that why her memory was wiped?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:57.66,0:10:00.54,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,{\i1}Or maybe she's just been putting on an act,
Dialogue: 10,0:10:01.17,0:10:02.37,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,{\i1}and she really...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:19.43,0:10:20.43,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:20.43,0:10:22.14,Default,Yasuda,0,0,0,,My name is Yasuda.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:22.14,0:10:26.42,Default,Yasuda,0,0,0,,I was the head of Yamasaki Factory's\nresearch and development department.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:26.42,0:10:27.94,Default,Yasuda,0,0,0,,The Humanoid division.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:29.16,0:10:31.82,Default,Yasuda,0,0,0,,I do apologize for interrupting your busy schedule,
Dialogue: 10,0:10:31.82,0:10:34.70,Default,Yasuda,0,0,0,,but could you spare a few minutes for a little chat?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:38.41,0:10:40.93,Default,Yasuda,0,0,0,,Terrible weather, isn't it?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:41.55,0:10:43.80,Default,Yasuda,0,0,0,,That leg of yours must\ntake badly to all this moisture.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:43.80,0:10:47.33,Default,Yasuda,0,0,0,,Believe me, I know how it is. I'm the same way.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:47.33,0:10:50.23,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Let's skip the pleasantries\nand get straight to the point.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:50.75,0:10:53.22,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Was Atri the one who got violent at that school?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:13.34,0:11:17.24,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,I trust you recognize this sequence.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:17.54,0:11:19.59,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Atri's logbook...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:22.62,0:11:25.72,Default,Yasuda,0,0,0,,YHN-04B-009. {period?}
Dialogue: 10,0:11:25.72,0:11:28.95,Default,Yasuda,0,0,0,,That unit's official serial number.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:29.72,0:11:35.36,Default,Yasuda,0,0,0,,The fourth generation was designed\nto record written logs in an effort to emulate
Dialogue: 10,0:11:35.36,0:11:39.23,Default,Yasuda,0,0,0,,a more human-like approach to\nmemory formation and knowledge acquisition.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:40.45,0:11:43.70,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,"Today, I met my first master.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:44.68,0:11:46.35,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Her name is—
Dialogue: 10,0:11:49.02,0:11:50.65,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Shiina..."
Dialogue: 10,0:11:51.23,0:11:52.64,Default,Yasuda,0,0,0,,A familiar name, I'm sure.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:55.53,0:11:57.10,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:57.10,0:11:58.39,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,This can't be real!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:06.78,0:12:10.22,Default,Yasuda,0,0,0,,The act of creating a true copy of our fellow man.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:10.22,0:12:13.34,Default,Yasuda,0,0,0,,Is that the apotheosis of scientific progress,
Dialogue: 10,0:12:13.34,0:12:16.49,Default,Yasuda,0,0,0,,or is it a sacred and inviolable taboo?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:16.49,0:12:20.76,Default,Yasuda,0,0,0,,The answer to that question\nwas Professor Konishi's life work.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:22.26,0:12:23.76,Default,Yasuda,0,0,0,,Konishi...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:23.76,0:12:25.60,Default,Yasuda,0,0,0,,My mentor.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:25.60,0:12:28.51,Default,Yasuda,0,0,0,,The man who created {\i1}that{\i0} Humanoid.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:28.51,0:12:30.35,Default,Yasuda,0,0,0,,The same Humanoid whose unprompted rampage
Dialogue: 10,0:12:30.35,0:12:33.39,Default,Yasuda,0,0,0,,ended his career and forever sullied his legacy.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:34.65,0:12:39.17,Default,Yasuda,0,0,0,,I consider it my duty to recover\nevery copy of that defective model
Dialogue: 10,0:12:39.17,0:12:41.38,Default,Yasuda,0,0,0,,and see that they are disposed of.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:42.28,0:12:46.77,Default,Yasuda,0,0,0,,A courtesy through which I hope to\nrepay my debt to the world and the late professor.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:48.09,0:12:51.01,Default,Yasuda,0,0,0,,May I count on your cooperation in this matter?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:55.98,0:12:57.81,Default,Yasuda,0,0,0,,Yours is the very last one.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:57.81,0:13:01.93,Default,Yasuda,0,0,0,,Once I dispose of that unit,\nmy work will be complete.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:02.71,0:13:04.57,Default,Yasuda,0,0,0,,I understand how you must feel.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:04.57,0:13:07.85,Default,Yasuda,0,0,0,,The fourth generation truly was impeccably made.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:07.85,0:13:10.49,Default,Yasuda,0,0,0,,Their algorithms for\ncomprehending human emotion
Dialogue: 10,0:13:10.49,0:13:14.74,Default,Yasuda,0,0,0,,are sophisticated enough to uphold\nthe deception that they are capable of empathy.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:15.29,0:13:19.25,Default,Yasuda,0,0,0,,But they have {\i1}absolutely nothing{\i0}\nresembling a true human heart.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:21.07,0:13:23.61,Default,Yasuda,0,0,0,,Surely you must have realized this too.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:23.61,0:13:27.47,Default,Yasuda,0,0,0,,That no matter how strong or sincere,\nyour feelings will never be able to reach it. {?}
Dialogue: 10,0:13:27.47,0:13:29.83,Default,Yasuda,0,0,0,,I assure you, your current path
Dialogue: 10,0:13:30.48,0:13:32.79,Default,Yasuda,0,0,0,,is a long road that leads only to heartbreak. {these two lines, the heart metaphor ofc, but "the only heart to break will be your own" sort of makes no sense...?}{I read it as "Only one of you two has a heart, and it's going to break" -yon}
Dialogue: 10,0:13:38.25,0:13:42.15,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,I... need some time to think.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:04.25,0:14:05.32,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:05.85,0:14:07.49,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Welcome home.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:10.87,0:14:13.02,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,You're acting different today.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:13.02,0:14:15.82,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,I am acting in accordance with your last orders.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:15.82,0:14:20.21,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,If I told you to act like you always do, would you?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:20.21,0:14:21.92,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,I will follow orders.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:24.89,0:14:25.93,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,It's an order, then.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:25.93,0:14:28.18,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Act like you always do.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:30.61,0:14:32.53,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Welcome home, Natsuki{**-san}!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:32.53,0:14:34.94,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Did you work up a big appetite today?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:36.70,0:14:39.36,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Yeah. Come to think of it,\nI haven't eaten anything all day.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:39.67,0:14:41.69,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Oh dear, we can't have that now!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:41.69,0:14:43.11,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Just one moment please!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:43.11,0:14:47.24,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Allow me to heat up your\nsecond helping of mom's cooking!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:47.24,0:14:48.87,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Curry, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:48.87,0:14:51.54,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,H-How'd you know?!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:51.54,0:14:54.67,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Curry's the classic day-after-nikujaga meal.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:55.60,0:14:57.26,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,They use all the same ingredients.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:57.26,0:15:00.71,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,I had no idea! You really know\nso many things, Natsuki{**-san}!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:05.55,0:15:06.20,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Atri.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:06.20,0:15:07.27,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:07.98,0:15:09.92,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Stop pretending like you have a heart.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:18.15,0:15:19.03,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Affirmative.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:25.62,0:15:26.86,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Dinner is served.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:45.52,0:15:47.20,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,How does it taste?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:47.99,0:15:49.39,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,If I said it was good,
Dialogue: 10,0:15:50.06,0:15:52.15,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,would it make you happy?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:54.26,0:15:54.60,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:54.60,0:15:55.35,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Bullshit!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:55.79,0:15:57.28,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,You wouldn't be {\i1}happy!{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:15:57.28,0:16:00.75,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,You'd just register that your AI\nmade the right decision!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:02.46,0:16:04.15,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,That is correct.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:05.05,0:16:06.90,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,I am a Humanoid.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:08.30,0:16:09.64,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,I apologize.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:11.15,0:16:12.49,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:13.16,0:16:14.78,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,I'm the one who should apologize.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:15.41,0:16:19.21,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,I shouldn't expect {\i1}anyone{\i0} to know\nhow to react to my nonsense.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:19.21,0:16:20.11,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:22.39,0:16:24.06,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Are you going out?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:24.06,0:16:25.67,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,I want to be alone.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:25.67,0:16:27.15,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Don't follow me.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:47.82,0:16:49.37,Default,Subordinate A,0,0,0,,What's the plan?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:53.55,0:16:56.45,Default,Radio,0,0,0,,Heavy rainfall is expected to continue
Dialogue: 10,0:16:56.45,0:16:59.17,Default,Radio,0,0,0,,as a low pressure system develops\ninto further severe weather.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:59.17,0:17:03.29,Default,Radio,0,0,0,,With heavy winds forecasted for coastal areas,\nships are advised to...{timing lacks a lead-out intentionally -Pik}
Dialogue: 10,0:17:22.01,0:17:23.06,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,What was that?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:27.45,0:17:28.86,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,I've been washed out!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:28.86,0:17:30.35,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,This is bad...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:37.48,0:17:38.58,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,What the...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:45.38,0:17:46.09,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Atri!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:08.47,0:18:13.42,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Ririka came to tell me the school is in danger.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:13.42,0:18:15.27,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,I have left to go with her.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:17.92,0:18:18.99,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,The notebook...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:19.63,0:18:20.89,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Shit!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:36.86,0:18:37.80,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:38.52,0:18:40.59,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's how it is, isn't it?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:41.69,0:18:43.56,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Why didn't I understand
Dialogue: 10,0:18:43.95,0:18:45.12,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,something so...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:49.11,0:18:49.86,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Atri...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:50.98,0:18:52.36,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Atri!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:02.09,0:19:03.62,Default,Miyo,0,0,0,,{*}Missus Hana{*Hana-chan-sensei}!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:03.62,0:19:06.12,Default,Catherine,0,0,0,,If you lay one finger on my kids, I swear...{Tricky... "Let my damn kids go!"?}
Dialogue: 10,0:19:06.12,0:19:08.08,Default,Yasuda,0,0,0,,By all means, relax.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:08.08,0:19:11.30,Default,Yasuda,0,0,0,,They will be free to go\nas soon as that Humanoid arrives.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:13.83,0:19:15.97,Default,Yasuda,0,0,0,,Don't be afraid. It'll all be over soon.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:16.31,0:19:19.11,Default,Yoko,0,0,0,,Ririka went to go get Atri{**-chan}, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:19.11,0:19:21.84,Default,Ryuuji,0,0,0,,Yeah. They should be here any minute now.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:29.27,0:19:30.36,Default,Yasuda,0,0,0,,There you are...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:33.18,0:19:35.20,Default,Yasuda,0,0,0,,Where is your master?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:35.52,0:19:36.52,Default,Ryuuji,0,0,0,,Where's Natsu?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:36.52,0:19:38.91,Default,Ririka,0,0,0,,That's the thing! I couldn't find him!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:40.24,0:19:41.49,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,Natsu{**-kun}...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:41.92,0:19:43.12,Default,Yasuda,0,0,0,,Well, no matter.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:43.59,0:19:45.03,Default,Yasuda,0,0,0,,Come over here.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:58.48,0:20:00.47,Default,Toru and Miyo,0,0,0,,{*}Missus Hana{*Hana-chan-sensei}!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:01.87,0:20:05.38,Default,Catherine,0,0,0,,There, there. It's okay. Everything's okay now.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:06.23,0:20:09.19,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,What are you going to do with Atri{**-chan}?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:19.66,0:20:21.17,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,Atri{**-chan}!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:25.30,0:20:28.17,Default,Yasuda,0,0,0,,Oh, the show's just getting started.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:28.17,0:20:32.15,Default,Yasuda,0,0,0,,I encourage all gathered here today to bear witness!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:32.15,0:20:35.01,Default,Yasuda,0,0,0,,To just how dangerous this Humanoid is...{He better have robot augmentations to his legs, core, shoulder, pectorals, and arms. Because if it's just his hand that's robotic, the strength of this punch makes no sense. -Pik}
Dialogue: 10,0:20:40.61,0:20:41.80,Default,Yoko,0,0,0,,Atri{**-chan}!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:42.18,0:20:43.31,Default,Ryuuji,0,0,0,,You son of a—
Dialogue: 10,0:20:46.88,0:20:48.48,Default,Subordinate,0,0,0,,Shut up and watch.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:51.01,0:20:52.48,Default,Yasuda,0,0,0,,Honestly...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:54.38,0:20:58.02,Default,Yasuda,0,0,0,,You disgrace the professor\nby attacking an innocent student
Dialogue: 10,0:20:58.02,0:21:00.20,Default,Yasuda,0,0,0,,and even manage to escape justice all this time.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:00.20,0:21:04.50,Default,Yasuda,0,0,0,,Just how much suffering\nmust you cause before you're satisfied?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:07.43,0:21:09.96,Default,Yasuda,0,0,0,,The professor gave you life,\nbrought you into this world,
Dialogue: 10,0:21:11.14,0:21:14.09,Default,Yasuda,0,0,0,,and {\i1}this{\i0} is how you chose to repay him?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:20.51,0:21:21.34,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,Atri{**-chan}!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:30.96,0:21:31.99,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Fuck...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:44.93,0:21:46.33,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,God dammit...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:46.99,0:21:48.08,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,God dammit!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:48.79,0:21:51.34,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,I need to...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:51.34,0:21:53.08,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Need to go find...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:53.53,0:21:58.09,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,I need to go find that stupid worthless robot! {two-bit?}
Dialogue: 10,0:21:59.64,0:22:02.03,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,She'd probably throw a tantrum\nif she heard me say that...
Dialogue: 10,0:22:03.54,0:22:07.10,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,She can't stop bragging about her high specs\neven though she only ever screws up...
Dialogue: 10,0:22:10.63,0:22:15.69,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,She's annoying as hell,\nand way too meddlesome for her own good...
Dialogue: 10,0:22:16.46,0:22:19.75,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,But she's got has a heart\nmore beautiful than any human's...
Dialogue: 10,0:22:19.75,0:22:22.61,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,And she's my piece-of-crap Humanoid!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:27.53,0:22:30.04,Default,Yasuda,0,0,0,,You defective {\i1}wretch{\i0}.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:30.04,0:22:32.57,Default,Yasuda,0,0,0,,If it weren't for you, the professor...
Dialogue: 10,0:22:32.57,0:22:35.04,Default,Yasuda,0,0,0,,If not! For you!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:35.04,0:22:37.25,Default,Yasuda,0,0,0,,He'd still be—!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:41.58,0:22:45.76,Default,Yasuda,0,0,0,,If only you'd never existed, everything would've...
Dialogue: 10,0:22:54.98,0:22:55.77,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Atri!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:56.06,0:22:57.15,Default,Catherine,0,0,0,,That's enough.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:58.10,0:22:59.61,Default,Catherine,0,0,0,,You've had your fun.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:59.61,0:23:02.58,Default,Yasuda,0,0,0,,What? Surely you jest!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:02.58,0:23:05.11,Default,Yasuda,0,0,0,,This is a {\i1}Humanoid{\i0}.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:05.11,0:23:07.16,Default,Yasuda,0,0,0,,Nothing of any concern.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:08.48,0:23:10.91,Default,Yasuda,0,0,0,,Isn't that right?{I don't get it. Does Atri need to breathe? -Pik}
Dialogue: 10,0:23:10.91,0:23:11.87,Default,Catherine,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:12.17,0:23:17.75,Default,Yasuda,0,0,0,,In the end, the only thing you were ever good for\nwas tricking humans to empathize with you...
Dialogue: 10,0:23:17.75,0:23:20.63,Default,Yasuda,0,0,0,,Really, you terrify me!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:20.63,0:23:21.88,Default,Yasuda,0,0,0,,You worthless,
Dialogue: 10,0:23:22.50,0:23:24.55,Default,Yasuda,0,0,0,,damnable monster!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:26.79,0:23:27.87,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Atri!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:34.93,0:23:37.43,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,{=5}Natsuki{**-san}...

